content.en:
If your operators have reached max potential, go to the [Acquisition Center - Quota Exchange] to convert their extra tokens into [AIC Quota] and [Endpoint Quota]. The following lists the exchange rates:
A [token] of a max-potential 6★ operator: [Endpoint Quota]×10;
A [token] of a max-potential 5★ operator: [AIC Quota]×20;
A [token] of a max-potential 4★ operator: [AIC Quota]×5.
